subject: Tennis
Wimbledon Tennis Tournament
lead_paragraph: As Hewitt faced Jarkko Nieminen at Wimbledon, someone’s sentimental journey had to end, and it turned out to be Hewitt’s despite the Australian extending the fifth set after saving two match points.
